## Martin_Stahl
### Sep 30, 2016
#### #6
Really, alerts are a nice feature but probably shouldn't be relied on too much. If you have a number of games, where it's your move , it is probably best to verify how much time is on each one, when on. I have lost a few no-vaction tourney games when I neglected to double check and thought I had more time than I actually had. I'm not saying the alert feature shouldn't be more robust.

